  UpgradeType: 1
  WeaponType: 3
  DamageType: 1
  UpgradeName: Splitter Shotgun
  UpgradeDescription:
  - Deploy a smaller turret that deals shotgun damage to enemies once within proximity
    range.
  - Increase proximity range by 25%
  - Increase damage scaling by 25% and knockback by 40%
  - Successfully hit bullets will now bounce 2 additional bullets behind enemies,
    dealing damage to enemies behind
  - Increase number of shotguns blast to 8
  - Increase damage scaling by 50%, now bounce 3 bullets and decrease ability cooldown
    by 20%
  MaxLevel: 6
  ID: 4
  ElitePath:
  - EliteUpgradeName: Charged Blast
    UpgradeDescription:
    - Additionally fire 1 projectile that explode and release blast of bullets in
      cone range
    - Damage +25%
    - Expand cone range into a wide arc
    - ' Ability cooldown +20%'
    - Fire 3 projectiles instantly instead of 1
    AlternateID: 1
    MaxLevel: 6
  - EliteUpgradeName: Auto Fire Buckshot
    UpgradeDescription:
    - 'Now become a fully automatic weapon Rapidly fire 6 shots then reload in 1s '
    - Damage +20%
    - Shots +7
    - Knock back +3
    - 'Increase damage dealt to the same target per hit, up to 50% '
    AlternateID: 1
    MaxLevel: 6
